	<brief_description>
        Abstract base class for interpreting flatbuffer serialised data.
    </brief_description>
	<description>
        This base class is to be overridden by code generated from the flatc schema compiler.
        It provides utilities for the generated gdscript overloads to interpret binary data in [member bytes] in the
        manner described schema file.
        This [FlatBuffer] object is a non owning view of the [PackedByteArray].
	</description>
